content: Improperly Manufactured Front Axle May Fail

Oshkosh Corporation (Oshkosh) is recalling certain 2024-2025 S-Series vehicles.  The front axle housing wall thickness may not be sufficient and can cause the axle to fail.Front axle failure can cause a sudden loss of vehicle handling and control, increasing the risk of a crash.

Number of Units Affected: 469.0
